data.description: GREAT SHORT OR LONG TERM RENTAL, INVESTMENT, VACATION HOME, OR PRIMARY RESIDENCE. Gorgeous and spacious Mediterranean style townhome with 4 Bedroom, 2 Bath. The Master bedroom is located on 1st floor with 3 bedroom, 1 Bathroom and Laundry on 2nd floor. Upgraded kitchen with wood cabinets, granite counters and stainless appliances. Tile throughout the main living areas and carpet upstairs. The clubhouse is equipped with a gym, heated pool as well as a playroom. Minutes from shopping and restaurants and attractions.
